{"tid":1458583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"心理戰 民意戰 全面展開!","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:43:58.000Z","uid":80972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"09c4d1a550242891c12cb8ebf2d28c6f7f905869","tid":1458583,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"中共已經開始上崗上線，話有恐怖主義嘅苗頭。我認為勇武風險愈來愈高，亦因為我地一直勇武升級唔多，先會有內鬼出黎帶風向，<span style=\"color: orange;\">分裂手足</span>。<br />\n<br />\n機場今日都已經好多討論，我唔再講。<br />\n我想講我地唔應該要塞鐵，令大家返唔到工，令佢地都嬲示威者。我地係要民意，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">令更多人企係我地呢邊!</span></span><br />\n令更多人逐步對政權反抗!<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地只要更多人一齊以小步伐，參與反政權運動，佢地就會愈來愈支持!</span></span><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n比如<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1)令全民免費搭港鐵，免費過隧道!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2) 帶親友去連儂場，甚或去示威<br />\n<br />\n總之用佢可接受嘅方法一步一步參與運動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原理係咁<br />\nNetflix 有套Derren Brown: Pushed to the Edge，設計令普通人去殺人就係<span style=\"color: orange;\">首先令佢做d好簡單嘅野，等佢個錯愈來愈多</span>，最後就會聽話去殺人。我地唔係去殺人，但要好多和非再支持我地，就要令佢地更覺得犯法係無野，政權係可以反對!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n今日好多謝原位去過機場嘅良心市民<br />\n今日冇人被捕冇人受傷就令機場停止運作<br />\n機場可以繼續進攻但必須hit and run同防內鬼搞事"},{"pid":"8314436d2780efc29f9dff945be0f6737f9312b7","tid":1458583,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"[賽後檢討] 抗爭者進化史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c79248f1ca4cd2e3fd0ad01fff8af885a144c8fa","tid":1458583,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:27:58.000Z","msg":"Darren Brown 傳送門<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/title/80220000?s=a&amp;trkid=13747225&amp;t=cp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftitle%2F80220000%3Fs%3Da%26trkid%3D13747225%26t%3Dcp&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=326847b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.netflix.com/title/80220000?s=a&amp;trkid=13747225&amp;t=cp</a>"},{"pid":"7d10de0a76ac4b430b5553be3bc9cacf8b0f2112","tid":1458583,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:28:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aeec9c95960ee33a385f07e22591857fdee1d71b","tid":1458583,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n幫手支持廣獨，將革命思想傳入中國！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ehx7Ac4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fehx7Ac4.jpg&h=3f367942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打可以用下面條link去印，set左a5 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1L7b5VnA5YwhI63YCK-55SGRKkF6GF4jV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1L7b5VnA5YwhI63YCK-55SGRKkF6GF4jV&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlcbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=218f5635\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1L7b5VnA5YwhI63YCK-55SGRKkF6GF4jV</a>"},{"pid":"9f1999e6665c15fc59435a73d49a9921c503f439","tid":1458583,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"re-post:<br />\n<br />\n正如賣廣告 sell 你嘢，<br />\n一定係刺激你想買嘢嘅 desire，<br />\nemotion-based<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bq828A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bq828A.jpg&h=25fa646a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從來唔會講道理講 logic，<br />\n因為一講，要用你錢，你點會捨得買？"},{"pid":"525ce6af64cd9ea228924ee186ec33983fb6c81f","tid":1458583,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:31:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"581b58858be782413df21bd37199dfa2272b5c37","tid":1458583,"uid":41355,"like":